The paper deals with the problem of extracting information from handwritten documents, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed approach uses a neural network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper presents experimental results, which could also be relevant to the information retrieval (cs.IR) community.
